<style>
  .article_column-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  img.article_column-image {
    overflow: hidden;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
  }
  .article_column-image-border {
    border: 1px solid rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
  }
  .article_column {
      height: max-content;
  }
  .article_column-third {
    width: calc(33.3333334% - 33.3333334px);
  }
  .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 25px);
  }
  .article_column-text-third-top {
    padding-top: 81px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 15px);
  }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .article_column-third {
        width: calc(50% - 15px);
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 81px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 950px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .article_column-half {
      width: 100%
    }
    .article_column-third {
        width: 100%;
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .rebranding_container {
        gap: 40px;
    }
    .article_column-text .h3-heading-pp, .article_column-text .h3-heading-ss {
        text-align: center;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 450px) {
    .article_column-image {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Balenciaga 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        authentication process
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      Authenticating a Balenciaga bag or accessory involves a detailed inspection of several key elements to ensure its authenticity and identify authentic bags. Here are the essential steps to follow:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-center">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-1.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Balenciaga authentication process">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 1</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Interior Label</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         Authentic Balenciaga bags feature a leather tab or metal plate inside, usually sewn along the back wall of the interior. This label includes key details like the <strong>style number and serial numbe</strong>r, which are essential for verification. The stitching around the label should be neat and secure. If the label is missing, loosely attached, or poorly aligned, it may indicate a counterfeit.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-2.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Verify the Style Number and Serial Number to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 2</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Serial Number Verification</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Each Balenciaga bag includes a serial number that should match a known format used by the brand. Some tags also include seasonal codes like <strong>“FW”</strong> (Fall/Winter) or <strong>“SS”</strong> (Spring/Summer). A <strong>Balenciaga serial number check</strong> can help confirm the bag's authenticity. For more reliable results, consider using a <strong>Balenciaga authentication service</strong> or consulting a <strong>trusted Balenciaga verification service</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-3.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Inspect the Hardware to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 3</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Hardware Inspection</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Genuine Balenciaga hardware is made from high-quality materials, including solid zippers, studs, and buckles, often engraved with precise branding. The hardware should feel heavy and smooth, not flimsy or rough. Poor-quality or unbranded hardware is a major red flag. This step is essential when learning <strong>how to spot fake Balenciaga</strong> bags.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-4.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Examine the Stitching and Seams to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 4</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Stitching & Seams</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Authentic Balenciaga bags have <strong>clean, even stitching</strong> with no loose threads, skipped stitches, or glue residue. The seams should be perfectly aligned and tightly finished. Irregular or messy stitching is one of the easiest ways to identify a fake. High-quality <strong>Balenciaga stitching</strong> is a clear indicator of genuine craftsmanship.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "balenciaga_authentication-process-5.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Check the Logo and Branding to authenticate Balenciaga bag">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <p class="caption w-100">Step 5</p>
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Logo & Branding</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          The Balenciaga logo should be consistent in font, spacing, and placement. Pay close attention to the text alignment and depth of embossing or printing. Counterfeit bags often feature poorly spaced or slightly off logos. For added peace of mind, use <strong>online Balenciaga authentication</strong> tools or refer to expert <strong>Balenciaga authentication tips</strong> to ensure your branding matches official standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

